				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Er, not quite. $4017 has only one function - it controls the APU's frame timer. If D7 is set, it runs in a 5-step sequence (48Hz) for pitch bends, timers, etc.; if clear, it runs in a 4-step sequence (60Hz). Clearing D6 causes IRQs to be generated at the end of the 4-step sequence (but not the 5-step one, oddly enough, so setting D6 *or* D7 will turn them off).
<br />
<br />[Edit] Whoops, fixed a little bit</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
					
