						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Is 'ldx #0 stx $2000 stx $2001' safe before waiting for two vblanks?</div>
<br />
<br />It most certainly is; in fact, MANY licensed games do exactly this.
<br />It's definitely something you want to do, since otherwise the PPU will possibly be rendering garbage AND generating NMIs during those two frames.</div>

					
